Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the year After Colony 175...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...the leader of the colonies\Nwas assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Gundams were sent\Nto Earth to take revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, since OZ's activities\Nin space...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...took the form of cooperation\Nrather than control...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...the colonies decided\Nto accept OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The year After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As OZ moves to take over\Nboth Earth and outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gundams are labeled rebels\Nand are isolated from society.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With no place to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundams and\Ntheir pilots...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...must fight for a reason to\Nexist in the changing world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They missed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Intentionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Milliardo, there's one other\Nperson who understands me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Her feelings toward me have\Ngiven her split personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The actions you took\Nwere justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I'm about\Nto do is also justified!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're adjusting the ballast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go slowly.\NEasy does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some light on those rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly damaged, considering\Nthe battle it's been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Vessels approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This was just Heero's trick,\Nabandoning his Gundam at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...while he goes to space alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mobile suit submarine\Ncarrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprise that OZ would\Ncome here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't concern yourself\Nabout us mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have expertise as the former\NAlliance's Deep-Sea Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to send out the Pisces!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Object at 1 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Zero One.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, send out the Cancers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, open fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Propeller sound confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in! Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Discarding his Gundam\Nlike that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The foundation of our future\Nwill be built by these suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for mass-production.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry about\Ncost performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Resources in space are\Nunlimited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He treats the Space Colonies\Nlike old world colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be plundered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give him something\Nto remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Gundam you took apart\Nto try stealing our technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still interested\Neven after it was trashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Chief Engineer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I start making a mobile\Nsuit superior to the Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit rushing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of things\Nto take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in\Njust rebuilding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't used to have\Nany problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...with your principles\Nagainst war in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So why is there a need\Nfor armaments now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred years have passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...since the colonies were\Nexperimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel there's no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...but to avoid battle\Nby arming ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sally Po, formerly a\NMajor in the Alliance Military.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As a rebel organization\Nmember opposing OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...she's supported and led a\Nnumber of their maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also signs that\Nshe has the Gundams Zero One and Zero Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romefeller Foundation\Nthat controls OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the most powerful\Nentity on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say there are problems\Nwith that organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we wanted to\Nprotect the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why we've\Naccepted OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We chose the option that\Nwould give us more safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Armed struggle will continue\Non Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we chose\Nthis method of protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ is keeping the Gundam\Nengineers captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those on Earth opposing\NOZ think that OZ alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...is changing the world into\Na dangerous place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard that the engineers\Nhave already been executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot maintain our\Ndignity as a nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...unless we augment\Nour strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and eliminate the chance\Nof more rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our decision won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to understand\Nour reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The engineers have been\Nexecuted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this kind of fabricated\Nrumor we must fear the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also, natural resources{\i0}\N{\i1}and parts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...have been transported{\i0}\N{\i1}from the plant colonies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...as we begin mobile suits{\i0}\N{\i1}production...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...on the Lunar Plant, together{\i0}\N{\i1}with support from OZ.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We no longer have to fear{\i0}\N{\i1}the possibility of an invasion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Commander-in-Chief{\i0}\N{\i1}Treize and Colonel Une's help...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...this will mark the beginning{\i0}\N{\i1}of a new era for outer space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bunch of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones who planted\Nthe fear of war in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The colonies have suffered\Na history of humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't afraid of battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...that will allow colony\Nindependence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Hilde Schbeiker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've volunteered my services\Nfrom this colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're an OZ soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can be critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The work of the colony's\Nstudents speaks for itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our volunteer work at the Lunar\NPlant reflects our faith in OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I should\Napply, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The next military exam\Nis in one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give it\Na try if you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Count on it; I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're headed to the Lunar Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they using us as test pilots\Nfor the new models?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe as target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even OZ admits that we're\Npretty psyched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The objective of OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...and its mother organization,\NRomefeller...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...was to destroy the United\NEarth Sphere Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and take control of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't they take over\Nthe colonies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking over the defenseless\Ncolonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...would be like twisting\Na baby's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Zechs would be\Nable to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize is getting hungry\Nfor mortal combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And the overconfident\Ncolonies will realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...just how much stronger\NTreize is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All soldiers prepare to board{\i0}\N{\i1}ship on the double!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All soldiers prepare to board{\i0}\N{\i1}ship on the double!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:09:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, new volunteers\Nare to apply next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a look\Nat that application!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all filled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a fake!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's taken the Leo!\N- After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to start firing\Ninside the colony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is to destroy\Nthe Lunar Plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's too far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you retaliate,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'll have to kill you!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning shots are meaningless\Nagainst inexperienced fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's for the peace\Nof the colony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fighting for the peace\Nof the colony as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving in till it's in\Ntarget range!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're both fighting for{\i0}\N{\i1}the colonies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are we enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you pleading for your life?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I volunteered and pledged\Nmy loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to die any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so intense it\Nmakes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, get outta here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo Maxwell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought\Nyou were a Gundam pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to sacrifice\Nmy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need sympathy\Nfrom my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilde, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What "enemies" do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when is the colony\Nan organization fighting a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Alliance came from\NEarth to attack the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...smiles disappeared from\Npeople's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been fighting to help\Ngive back those smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I come back to the\Ncolony, and guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't want their\Nsmiles back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When did the colonies\Nget so twisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Outer space is affected by\Nthe war on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just sit back\Nand be taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is outer space's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bravery's commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Lunar Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be questioned on the\NGundam, among other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Saves me a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I'm planning\Nto destroy the Lunar Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you see me\Nas an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate to say this, but you don't\Nhave the skills to be my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's foolish for you to\Nrisk your life against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you remind me of how\Nreckless I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I went to Earth\Nto fight all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't patronize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we're both foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier can get killed\Nat any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see many friends in\Nthe colony lose their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's live our lives believing\Nin the paths we've chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be at least that\Nfoolish to make it as a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he tell you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...couldn't we have\Nfired a warning shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have orders to kill rebels\Nwhen necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what wars are about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means sacrificing\Nyour own people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer Hilde.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But soldiers must always\Nbe prepared to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...to fulfill their missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unit Chief, we're about to{\i0}\N{\i1}arrive at the Lunar Base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take the shuttle to OZ's\Nmilitary establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To deliver the prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The third engine's on fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone on board did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got good instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back if you don't\Nwanna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that explosion?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?! Report!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The mass balance device\Nis busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get seasick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:15:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it to the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ironic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I washed-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too bad a job,\Nif I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and finish me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the thought of being\Nkilled by a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give your code to prove\Nyou're an ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling who\Nmy allies are anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Duo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry up and do what{\i0}\N{\i1}you want to accomplish!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilde...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to live out my life,\Nbelieving in my chosen path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hilde.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'm not\Nbailing you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm already\Nprepared to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hilde!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't die in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing, Hilde?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drop your gun at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got a serious problem{\i0}\N{\i1}with your conduct!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to the plant\Nthrough this duct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe the enemy\Nhas entered Area B6!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Call from a colony Unit Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is attempting to\Ndestroy the mobile suit plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get security underground\Nand stop him from entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to kill us, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So it WAS you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then those are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're new models.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo, how would you like\Nto operate one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When's it finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you live\Nuntil it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll have your\Nchance in the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo, decide quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them\Nfind this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll do it your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you do the honors?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I hate to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't hurt as much if\Nyou screamed out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming here and trying to\Nkill us, after all we've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let anyone\Ninterfere with our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Botched your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't destroy the base...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you didn't kill\NDr. J and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rub it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still glad I decided\Nto come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Gundam and mine\Nare being rebuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like OZ will be\Nkeeping us alive for the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good chance,\Nso don't die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan on dying\Nthat easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the colonies\Nto fight for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the God of Death again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've completed my mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...to escort Ambassador\NPeacecraft on his return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Ambassador\Nrealizes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...how resolved the people\Nin space are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How about from the eyes\Nof Zechs Merquise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He has opinions about\Nthis era as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll battle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hear his decision then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone\Ncan stop the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:22:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll try to direct things\Ntoward Treize's ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sacrifice my life\Nfor that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For Treize's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And for my own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is destruction the only path\Nfor an outer space gone mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit resembling\Na Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...attacks the colonies that\Nare arming themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa and Heero head out\Nto face this powerful new suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They find that the pilot of\Nthis mobile suit is Quatre...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...cold with anger and\Nfull of deep sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 24,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Gundam They Called Zero".
